title: Home
text:
Hello, my name is Nathanaël Soulage, I am currently a student enrolled in the Research Master’s in Economics at Sciences Po Paris. I am willing to pursue research in Economics, therefore this website is designed to present and share my work, projects and skills.
I hold a Bachelor’s degree in Political and Social Sciences from Sciences Po Paris, with a major in Economics. I am now in my second year of Research Master’s degree in Economics, graduating in June 2025. For more details you can find my resume here.
Many thanks to the amazing Paulo Gugelmo Cavalheiro Dias, who created a wonderful tutorial to create your own Research Portfolio
